{"tid":1285074,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"洛迪竟然仲住緊大學宿舍","createTime":"2019-07-04T12:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T06:11:14.000Z","uid":199590,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1e138210f2f5263c3986d18ac544f56a8045a1","tid":1285074,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:14:04.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼城剛以高達7000萬歐元買斷馬德里體育會中場洛迪卡斯簡迪，他的朋友靴拿利祖就大爆其私生活跟一般球員大有分別。<br />\n<br />\n22歲的洛迪卡斯簡迪（Rodri）雖然已經名成利就，但仍然十分看重學業；修讀商業經濟的他從未錯過任何一課，而且仍然住在大學宿舍，「剛開始時，大家看到洛迪打乒乓球及洗衣服時都十分震驚。」<br />\n<br />\n靴拿利祖指，洛迪就算成為了職業球員，亦已入選了西班牙國家隊，但這些成就都沒有令他改變，仍然腳踏實地：「洛迪經常都說，他的生活不只得足球，希望可以跟正常人一樣過日子。」<br />\n<br />\n「洛迪的汽車仍然是那輛二手的Opel Corsa。他們建議洛迪買更好的，但他不明白為甚麼要花錢於汽車之上。他說有些朋友瘋狂買車，但他認為車只是用來從A點去到B點，就此而已。」靴拿利祖續說。"},{"pid":"0357146e78baa2a4474dc79a29320d67fe61a1ee","tid":1285074,"uid":200758,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e98f8098faad902de21568daf7f678f6be05c09","tid":1285074,"uid":64464,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"白人版簡迪"},{"pid":"b9e3dd503085a07ce5db6be4072c361c3fff1c94","tid":1285074,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PjEzWPp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPjEzWPp.png&h=0a034c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y7CmBPp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY7CmBPp.png&h=4384da28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b45f3ffaba977aa80c059a24e398af35e9bfd3d2","tid":1285074,"uid":15830,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"好過周圍fing一退休就老破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c3c7ebd